Global to raise funds via private placement . Philippines ' Global Equities Inc said on Tuesday its board of directors had approved a plan to raise 347 . 364 million pesos through a private placement of shares . Assistant corporate secretary Anna Melissa Rosario told the Philippine Stock Exchange that it would issue 231 , 576 , 082 shares at 1 . 50 pesos per share to strategic investors . The holding company , which has stakes in an electronic firm , a cotton company , a cement manufacturing plant , and several real estate projects , did not say where it would use the proceeds of the sale . The sale of the shares are still subject to the approval of the Securities and Exchange Commission and the Philippine Stock Exchange . Global closed at 2 . 04 pesos per share on Tuesday . - Manila newsroom 63 2 8418938 Fax 8176267 
